.. -*- restructuredtext -*-

User Accounts
=================
This app enables user account management.

Features
=================

 1. Create Account

    1. Via Admin Interface
    2. Via manage.py command
    3. Via shell scripts


 2. Edit Account Details

    1. Via Admin Interface

 3. Change Password

    1. Via Admin Interface
    2. Via manage.py command

 4. Reset Forgotten Password

    1. Via Admin Interface
    2. Self-service via web

 5. Deactivate/Reactivate Accounts

    1. Via Admin Interface

 6. Delete Accounts

    1. Via Admin Interface
